text: Podolsky () is a rural locality (a village) in Maysky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 67 km from Iglino, 10 km from Maysky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Podolsky, Republic of Bashkortostan
